Package us.ihmc.euclid.tools

Class TransformationTools

  • java.lang.Object
    • us.ihmc.euclid.tools.TransformationTools
  • public class TransformationTools
extends java.lang.Object
    TransformationTools provides a list a methods for transforming geometry objects useful in particular contexts where the result cannot be stored in an object.

    Note that in common situations, the use of TransformationTools should be avoided preferring the use of the 'transform' or 'applyTransform' methods provided with the concerned objects. Also note that these methods are possibly more computationally expensive than their respective couterparts.

    Author:
    Sylvain Bertrand
